Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[imitates car revving]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Near, if you don't mind me asking,\Nwhat do you make of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.18,0:01:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm interested to hear\Nwhat your thoughts are on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] The current Kira is foolish\Nand overconfident,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,not to mention unusually cooperative\Nwith the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So much so, that I suspect\Nhe's working hand in hand with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-You think so?\N-That would make the second L and Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,one in the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-That can't be. Are you serious?\N-[Near] Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said that, I'll admit that\NI'm only seven percent certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:01:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Don't worry, Commander Rester,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,making assumptions\Nis part of any investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're wrong,\Nall it'll cost is an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[child] There have been less crimes lately\Nin Japan and around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My daddy told me\Nthat if you do something bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,your name will be written\Non the Internet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your name, please.\N-...and Kira will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I don't have all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to file this report\Nwithout your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break. Please, not my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone or I'll put your names\Non the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA, PLEASE KILL...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[tap dripping]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[man on radio] I will proclaim this\Nright here and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to all the people of the Earth,\NKira is true justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[jingle playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA'S KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening. It is my honor\Nto be appointed by Kira as his spokesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a hoax.\NIt's the absolute truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that there will be many people\Nwho might try to have me killed now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am prepared to risk my life\Nin order to spread Kira's vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,NEW JAPANESE TASK FORCE HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Kira's Kingdom, huh?\NWhat a horrible title.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ide] This is insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to capture Kira\Nis an unforgivable crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-If you happen to know anybody...\N-If anybody deserves to be killed by Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it's this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-...a criminal or a regular citizen...\N-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch it back to the press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-The president's about to start.\N-[audience applauding on TV]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-[camera shutters clicking]\N-[Matusda] I wonder what it's about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All they said was that it was gonna be\Nsome sort of international announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't do anything but watch TV,\Ndo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what? [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning,\NI'm gonna try to keep this brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-[Light] No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] The United States\Nwill no longer oppose Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-[all gasp]\N-[audience yelling indistinctly on TV]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Those cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I've done it! I've even brought\NAmerica to its knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the hell is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Have they been threatened or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that Kira is justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice? No, no, I never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But because of Kira, war and conflict\Nhave ceased to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Criminal organizations\Nare in a state of ruin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,not only in the United States,\Nbut in all free nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who defies Kira head on\Nwill be killed. That is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not acknowledging Kira\Nas a symbol of justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we are simply saying that, as a country,\Nwe will not take any actions against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[man 1 on TV] How is that any different?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[man 2 on TV] You're saying\Nthat you accept Kira? Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[man 3 on TV ] And you call yourself\Nthe representative of our country?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it. This is America!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How can their government do something\Nso cowardly like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… do you guys mind if I ask\Na serious question?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, what is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling us you're not\Nalways serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys ever think that maybe\NKira isn't completely evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-What kind of question is that, Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about it and part of me\Njust doesn't believe that he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you think Kira is justice too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think that Kira's trying to fight\Nevil and change the world in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And well, the world's become a good place\Nfor people who live honest lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-so, maybe--\N-You're wrong, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,People are only afraid\Nof losing their own lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you think that's real peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that! Believe me,\NI know that as well as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I can also understand\Nthe other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see why all those people\Ncall Kira a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] When it comes down it,\NI've always been a really weak person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm also a detective.\NI can't accept Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's my duty to catch him.\NNo, I want to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I can't completely\Nhate him either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I must be crazy or something, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] No, you're not crazy.\NYou're normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[all] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Light?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'm sure that on some level,\NKira probably knows
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-that what he's doing is evil.\N-[Ryuk cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But he'll try to change the world\Neven as a martyr, at the cost of his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his brand of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that's what's going\Nthrough Kira's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we shouldn't be arguing about it.\NGood or evil, it's not our call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to think about\Nis catching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kira gets caught,\Nthen that makes him evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he wins and rules the world,\Nthen I guess he's justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] But from now on, the world\Nwill start leaning in favor of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time.\NKira will be justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni]\NWhat's going to happen to us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] It looks like we've been disbanded\Nthanks to that chicken of a president.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's not even a chicken.\NHe's less than a maggot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way accepting Kira\Nwill lead to anything good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[shower water splashing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-What should we do?\N-Let him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mello, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello snarls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Everyone, please put away\Nyour guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a shoot-out here\Nwould achieve nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, with all due respect,\NMello's the one who killed our partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Please don't make me\Nsay it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that our primary objective\Nis still to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing Mello right now will do nothing\Nto benefit our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like things have been going\Njust as you planned, Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes. I take it you've already\Nheard all about the second L
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,from Lidner by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've pretty much figured out who Kira is\Nand it's mostly thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-to everything you've done.\N-[Mello growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[cocking gun] Shut up, Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not just a tool for you to use\Nin order to solve your puzzles, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mello, if you really wanna shoot me\Nthen go ahead and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! If you shoot him,\Nthen the rest of us will have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but to shoot you too.\NWhat will it solve if both of you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what Kira wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm only here for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to take back\Nthat photograph you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Of course.\NI got it from the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There was only one\Nand no copies have been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already gone ahead and dealt\Nwith everyone who knows your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,both inside and outside Wammy's house.\NThey'll keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say a hundred percent for certain,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but it shouldn't be possible\Nfor you to be killed by the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Is that the only business\Nyou had with me, Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Near…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[bells chiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Let's get one thing straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of working together\Nwith you on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, I can't just take\Nmy photo and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't be right.\NSo I'll settle my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] The killer notebook...\Nit belongs to a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever touches it\Nis able to see a god of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell would believe\Nin something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I would. I believe him completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What good would it do for him\Nto tell an outrageous lie like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he had something to gain,\Nhe could at least come up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,with a more believable story.\NTherefore, these gods of death must exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The notebook I obtained had previously\Nbelonged to another Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps even Kira himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, some of the rules written inside\Nare actually fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can tell you for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-Near?\N-Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of us is gonna reach Kira first,\NI wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The race is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] We're both headed\Ntowards the same destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near scoffs] Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Fake rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that the notebook\Ncan cause heart attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and control its victims to a degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As for burning it or tearing it up,\Nthe notebook still exists
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no way to confirm\Nthe rule one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The false rule must be the one\Nthat states a person will die
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,if he doesn't write a name\Nwithin 13 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Near] Gevanni.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Please set up a connection to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, sir.\N-[keyboard clicking]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-[beeping]\N-[Matusda] It's Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] L, I thought you should know\Nthat we caught Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-[all gasping]\N-But he escaped soon afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[all sighing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] We were able\Nto interrogate him for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't really escape, did he?\NYou let him get away. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we tried to restrain him\Nbut he was too quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Mello mentioned\Nthat there was some sort of Shinigami
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-attached to the notebook.\N-[gasps softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Have you been able to confirm\Nthe existence of such a creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I can tell you for a fact\Nthat Shinigami do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't share that information\Nwith you in the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was certain\Nyou would never believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I would like to ask the Shinigami\Na few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, I'm not up for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that's bothering me\Nthe most about this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is the issue of those rules\Nwritten in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have reason to believe\Nthat one of them is fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-[all] Huh?\N-[Light] A fake rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes. L, I'd be interested\Nto hear your thoughts on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of all the rules,\Nwhich do you think is the fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'd like to know.\N-[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By process of elimination,\Nthe obvious choice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,would be the one stating\Nthat the owner of the notebook will die
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,if they don't write a new name in it\Nevery 13 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I thought you might say so.\NI've reached the same conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Shinigami, you know the rules\Nof the notebook well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us. Are any of them false?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they are all real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I see. You have a Shinigami\Nthere with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm beginning to get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Kira is there in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's making the Shinigami lie\Non his behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Whoa, this guy's good.\NHe nailed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what he means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if the Shinigami's lying\Nand the rule's fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really change anything,\Ndoes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that Light's incarceration\Nwould be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The rule says you die\Nif you don't continue writing names,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but if that's false, being alive\Nafter 13 days in confinement
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't really prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if that's true,\Nit doesn't mean he's guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's no way\Nthat Light could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he passed away,\Nthe Deputy Director himself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,was able to confirm\Nthat he didn't have a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] If there's a problem,\NI suggest we verify the rule this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will volunteer to write down\NMello's real name in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Of course, that means he'll die.\NIf I also die 13 days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,well, then I guess Kira wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, it's a gamble\NI'm quite willing to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? So this is just a game to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near]\NTesting and confirming the 13-day rule
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,can only benefit the Kira investigation.\NAnd other than my possible death,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be no drawbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to put my life on the line\Nif it will help us solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] If I answer him based\Non my feelings alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll only make me look worse to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please wait for a moment?\NWe need to discuss your suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[microphone switch clicks]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. What are your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can say that we must respect\Nhuman life and deny this request...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't suggest that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one under suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tough call.\NMello killed the Deputy Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If Near is willing, I wouldn't stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm against the idea, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe that Kira's hiding\Namong us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't use the notebook,\Nno matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We should respect\Nthe Deputy Director's wishes to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same. I'm opposed to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Near, we've talked it over\Nand we can't allow you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to use the notebook like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I had a feeling you might say so.\NNo matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one last question before I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To the members\Nof the Japanese Task Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there ever a point\Nin the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where the second L was suspected\Nto be Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,even if the suspicions were later dropped?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've been listening\Nto our conversation so far
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and have any intention of helping\Nmy investigation and taking down Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then call the number\NI'm about to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Day or night, I will answer.\NThe choice is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] There's no way\Nthat Light could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's more like\NI don't wanna believe he's Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the 13-day rule is fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then we really can't say for sure\Nthat he's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This could change everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Near. I have to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, hello?\N-[automated Kira voice] This is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] If you want proof,\NI can read out a list of people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm going to punish tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, you can check it\Nand make your final decision afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, I am very grateful\Nthat you and your country
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,have sympathized with me, but I'm afraid\Neven that much isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The SPK is still trying to catch me\Ndespite your recent announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to stop them immediately,\Nand formally disband them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, I want you to use\Nthe American police, the CIA, the FBI,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and all other law enforcement\Norganizations at your disposal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to find out where the SPK members\Nare currently hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you've found\Ntheir base of operations,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to forward that information\Nto a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you this contact shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, whether you live\Na long life or not is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[hangs up]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[President groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-[man 1] Mr. Demegawa! Please wait!\N-[man 2] Why are you going to New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] We are going to crush\Nan organization that dares to defy Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be on live TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a direct order from Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and it came through the President\Nof the United States himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[all] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's gonna happen\Nwhen we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell, I don't even know what I'm saying\Nanymore, and I don't really care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura TV's ratings are gonna rocket\Nto 100, no, 120 percent for this special!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs maniacally]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone! The new age\Nof Kira is about to arrive! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] The previous L\Nwas suspicious of Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Light is Kira, and I just come out\Nand say we should investigate him again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably end up dead just like L,\Nand that won't solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The 13-day rule, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ide] Aizawa.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a long history. I can tell exactly\Nwhat you're thinking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and what's bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Between you and me, you should go ahead\Nand do what you think is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't trust L to begin with.\NI never did, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't sign up\Nto join the Kira task force
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because Light was running it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I joined because I wanted\Nto work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ide…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Alright. I'll see if I can\Ncontact Near without letting Light know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ide] Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure that no one knows\Nwhat you're doing. You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[both cough awkwardly]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, I really want to believe\Nthat you're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting] This is really bad!\NTurn on the TV! It's Demegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-[all] Huh?\N-[helicopter propeller thrumming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Demegawa, live.\NMy comrades and I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,have finally pinpointed the hideout\Nof the evil organization
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,bent on trying to catch\Nour beloved god, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We now have the building\Ncompletely surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-[mob yelling]\N-[man] Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] Break down the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] Right now, our enemies\Nappear to be hiding within the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But they won't be able to hide\Nfrom us for long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[mob yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] Behold the power of the people!\NThe power of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] As soon as Near escapes,\NI'm gonna write his name in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Light. I won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] At this rate, we'll be dragged\Noutside unless we stop them somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[monitors beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] L…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that this is some sort of plot\Nby Mello to finish off the SPK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Surely it couldn't be\Nthat the SPK's security
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,was so lax that even a normal citizen\Ncould find out where it was located?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[figurine snaps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Damn it.\NHe's lying through his teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light chuckling] I win, Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]